&nbsp;

[caption id="attachment_48327" align="alignnone" width="653"]<a href="https://castles.com.ng/2-bedroom-apartment-design-scheme-1/5-34/" rel="attachment wp-att-48327"><img class=" wp-image-48327" src="https://castles.com.ng/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/5-5-300x250.jpg" alt="" width="653" height="546" /></a> <br />This TV wall with the two-tone colour of the console and display ledges is pure art on its own. The spotlights add dramatic lighting to the composition. The large sliding door/window by the left throws in so much natural light into the space and the dining area at one corner makes this - home sweet home![/caption]

&nbsp;

[caption id="attachment_48326" align="alignnone" width="650"]<a href="https://castles.com.ng/2-bedroom-apartment-design-scheme-1/6-25/" rel="attachment wp-att-48326"><img class=" wp-image-48326" src="https://castles.com.ng/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/6-5-300x250.jpg" alt="" width="650" height="544" /></a> White upper cabinets give the kitchen a subtle and neat look, while the arrangement introduces some dynamism to the space. The eco-friendly bamboo lower cabinets are matched nicely with the drawn curtains in the corner, adding a nice little touch to this pastel-coloured interior. There is a seamless blend of all the elements in this kitchen; with everything well-arranged and in place, cooking is made easy![/caption]

&nbsp;

[caption id="attachment_48325" align="alignnone" width="635"]<a href="https://castles.com.ng/2-bedroom-apartment-design-scheme-1/7-9/" rel="attachment wp-att-48325"><img class=" wp-image-48325" src="https://castles.com.ng/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/7-1-300x250.jpg" alt="" width="635" height="531" /></a> Extra storage arrangements are replete here and for a two bedroom apartment, this is super luxury. The natural flow of colours (beige, light wood and white) within this space fosters a sense of unity with minimal clashing.[/caption]

&nbsp;

[caption id="attachment_48324" align="alignnone" width="665"]<a href="https://castles.com.ng/2-bedroom-apartment-design-scheme-1/8-10/" rel="attachment wp-att-48324"><img class=" wp-image-48324" src="https://castles.com.ng/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/8-2-300x250.jpg" alt="" width="665" height="556" /></a> The way the refrigerator is incorporated into the cabinetry, which runs from floor to ceiling is evidence that this is a clean, well-thought design! The recessed ceiling adds some depth, while the textures on the carrara backsplash keeps the ensemble visually exciting.[/caption]

&nbsp;

[caption id="attachment_48323" align="alignnone" width="663"]<a href="https://castles.com.ng/2-bedroom-apartment-design-scheme-1/9-8/" rel="attachment wp-att-48323"><img class=" wp-image-48323" src="https://castles.com.ng/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/9-2-300x250.jpg" alt="" width="663" height="555" /></a> The exquisite parquet flooring extends to the walls as skirting creating a wholesome look. The wardrobe and TV console with ledge above is just the right colour and size for this warm and cozy master bedroom. The black frames on the pictures above the TV are matched nicely with the window frame. Everything comes together in visual harmony![/caption]

&nbsp;

[caption id="attachment_48322" align="alignnone" width="661"]<a href="https://castles.com.ng/2-bedroom-apartment-design-scheme-1/10-3/" rel="attachment wp-att-48322"><img class=" wp-image-48322" src="https://castles.com.ng/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/10-300x250.jpg" alt="" width="661" height="553" /></a> The headboard and bedside drawers is simple and elegant, and the picture frames adorning the wall is a touch of class making this a real haven! The way the curtains are drawn, letting in so much daylight - it’s magnificent. The modern Edison lamp by the bed draws little attention to itself, the silky peach bedspread and the polished silver hardware of the wardrobe are minute details that all work together to make this bedroom look très beau![/caption]

&nbsp;

[caption id="attachment_48321" align="alignnone" width="663"]<a href="https://castles.com.ng/2-bedroom-apartment-design-scheme-1/11-6/" rel="attachment wp-att-48321"><img class=" wp-image-48321" src="https://castles.com.ng/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/11-300x250.jpg" alt="" width="663" height="555" /></a> This second bedroom is striking with the rounded-edge display ledge in bright wood colour that can easily take your favourite indoor potted plant or your exotic figurines from fond memories of your trip to Dubai. The subtle wood colour of the bed-frame with side drawers is beautiful and seated atop the stripe-patterned centre rug, the effect is dramatic. The spotlight draws attention to the dreamy sights of the Eiffel tower against a backdrop of tall buildings and tourists in autumn. This has to be a collector’s coven![/caption]

